<h4>User Stories</h4>

<ol>
  <li>As a visitor, I want to read some marketing propaganda on the home page.</li>
  <li>As a visitor, I want to sign up for a user account so that I can become a customer.</li>
  <li>As a user, I want to create a new task.</li>
  <li>As a user, I want to edit a task.</li>
  <li>As a user, I want to delete a task</li>
  <li>As a user, I want to update a task.</li>
  <li>As a user, I want to see all tasks created by me under My Account.</li>
  <li>As a user, I want to view all my tasks for a date on the Calendar.</li>
  <li>As a user, I want to see total time spent on a chosen date.</li>
</ol>


<h4>Business Rules</h4>

<ol>
  <li>A task has name, description, duration, level of importance, and completion date.</li>
  <li>User can only see tasks created by him/herself.</li>
  <li>Task name, description, duration, importance, and completion date cannot be null.</li>
  <li>Only signed up users can use the application.</li>
  <li>Each email address can only be used once for sign-up</li>
  <li>User passwords must be securely encrypted.</li>
</ol>
